\par }\qj\fi432\sb648\nowidctlpar\adjustright \f16\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-3\cgrid {Measured by the quantity of new books on folkloristic topics, }{\expnd0\expndtw2\cgrid the interest of the Japanese people in their own old folkways }{\expnd0\expndtw-1\cgrid 
must be wide-spread. These days we see not only the publication }{\expnd-1\expndtw-5\cgrid of monographs but also of a number of encyclopedias and source books on Japanese history and on folkloristic themes as well, all }{\expnd0\expndtw3\cgrid written by
 competent experts for the general public. It seems }{\expnd-1\expndtw-5\cgrid that great treasures of manuscripts have been accumulated during }{\expnd0\expndtw-2\cgrid the post-war years on the desks of scholars who have patiently }{waited for a chance 
to see heir findings published some time, and }{\expnd0\expndtw-2\cgrid the time must have come now. Books we have been able to read }{\expnd0\expndtw0\cgrid and study so far, do not give us the impression that they have }{\expnd0\expndtw-4\cgrid been com
piled by their writers upon invitation by publishers who }{want to meet the demand of the public. We find that many forces }{\expnd0\expndtw0\cgrid have been working all the time during the war and thereafter, }{\expnd0\expndtw4\cgrid forces that not only
 digested earlier publications for the sake }{\expnd0\expndtw-2\cgrid of popular editions but have made new advances in many fields. }{The way of the presentation of the subject matters has also im\-}{\expnd0\expndtw-1\cgrid proved. Furthermore, compared 
with the pre-war publications, }{\expnd0\expndtw2\cgrid there is a more objective attitude towards national folkways, }{\expnd-1\expndtw-5\cgrid higher methodological standards, and sometimes even a deep cut\-}{\expnd1\expndtw5\cgrid ting criticism of the
 established old ways of Folklore Science }{\expnd-1\expndtw-6\cgrid in this country. As we shall see, there are writers who want to put }{\expnd0\expndtw3\cgrid Folklore Science on an entirely new basis and to have it adopt }{\expnd0\expndtw2\cgrid a new
 world-wide outlook as an integral part of Cultural An\-}{\expnd0\expndtw0\cgrid thropology.
\par }\fi360\sb360\nowidctlpar\adjustright \expnd0\expndtw0\cgrid {In the present survey we have picked out some of the new }{\expnd-1\expndtw-5\cgrid books now on the market. We came across two new books on the }{\expnd0\expndtw-3\cgrid Japanese farmhous
